00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:26.750
That's harder work than trying to find

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:28.540
some math thing that fixes it.

00:12:28.540 --> 00:12:29.910
Math thing's not going to fix it.

00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:31.410
It's not going to fix it.

00:12:31.410 --> 00:12:33.590
The thing that's going to fix
it is when you fix you.

