00:19:50.550 --> 00:19:52.550
I mean, I tell people you could lose 40%

00:19:52.550 --> 00:19:55.000
or more of that money
to taxes and penalties.

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.510
So, you don't want to do that.

00:19:56.510 --> 00:19:58.060
You want to leave that money alone,

