00:20:08.360 --> 00:20:10.210
what you're trying to do is save up

00:20:10.210 --> 00:20:12.440
enough money to replace
your paycheck later.

00:20:12.440 --> 00:20:13.660
So the money you're putting in

00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:15.570
will become your paycheck later in life.

00:20:15.570 --> 00:20:17.010
But we need to let it sit there.

00:20:17.010 --> 00:20:19.000
Rachel, money has two best friends.

00:20:19.000 --> 00:20:22.470
- Ooh, BFFs.
