I mean, she had gone
through some life stuff.

00:30:08.810 --> 00:30:11.620
And I felt in that moment that
I knew what I was going to do.

00:30:11.620 --> 00:30:13.640
I knew I was going to leave a big tip.

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:16.270
Well, my son saw this
dollar amount that I put out

00:30:16.270 --> 00:30:17.560
and I said, "Alright, buddy, let's go."

00:30:17.560 --> 00:30:20.100
He goes, "No, dad, we
gotta wait on your change."

00:30:20.100 --> 00:30:21.530
And I'm like, "No, no."

00:30:21.530 --> 00:30:23.230
Now, you all know I can't whisper, right?

00:30:23.230 --> 00:30:26.200
I've been banned in 48 of the
