00:30:26.200 --> 00:30:28.530
But I'm trying to get him
out before she comes back

00:30:28.530 --> 00:30:29.860
because have you ever had somebody

00:30:29.860 --> 00:30:31.300
try to block your blessing?

00:30:31.300 --> 00:30:32.174
You know, you try to do something nice?

00:30:32.174 --> 00:30:33.070
- Yeah, yeah, yeah,
yeah, totally, totally.

00:30:33.070 --> 00:30:34.690
- Well, it creates awkwardness, right?

